      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been a super reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it drives!",
