      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking great and running smoothly. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
