      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit remains a purist's choice with a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response, pulling cleanly to its 8,250 RPM redline. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system operate within peak parameters. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing versatile damping rates for both spirited cornering and daily compliance. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain uncompromised.",
